title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Leber/Bercich/Charch/Sinykin/Johnny Athletic/JG
description: Jam packed show today as a slew of guests stop by to break down the Vikings week 3 win over the Seahawks, Nordo checks in with Dave Sinykin to discuss the Packers, plus a little Timberwolves talk with Johnny Athletic.
